{"tid":1939130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】塞爾維亞總統迎中國物資專機 親吻五星旗","createTime":"2020-03-23T03:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T23:03:48.000Z","uid":271829,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1865ebb28cc20aaa92483906fca7e5bdba2a05","tid":1939130,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200322/4OMKTTYW35SKLF6UDLD5OKPISU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200322%2F4OMKTTYW35SKLF6UDLD5OKPISU%2F&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=64b906dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200322%2F4OMKTTYW35SKLF6UDLD5OKPISU%2F&h=908b0314\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200322/4OMKTTYW35SKLF6UDLD5OKPISU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200322/large/1584878663_34cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200322%2Flarge%2F1584878663_34cf.jpg&h=a39d4f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情全球肆虐，西班牙、菲律賓、塞爾維亞等國早前向最先爆發疫情的中國尋求支援。中國一架載着6名醫療隊專家以及十幾噸防疫物資的專機，當地時間21日晚上7時許，飛抵塞爾維亞機場。根據央視轉播的畫面，塞爾維亞總統武契奇（Aleksandar Vučić），到場接機時親吻在場掛着的五星旗，引起外界熱議。有中國網民指，塞爾維亞至少不會「反咬我們一口，其他西方國家很難說」，也有人嘲諷，這猶如「斯德哥爾摩症候群」。<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體報道，中國這架馳援塞爾維亞的專機，上面載有十幾噸的呼吸機、口罩、試劑盒等防疫物資。塞爾維亞總統武契奇、衞生部長、國防部長等多位政府官員，均親自到停機坪等候，並與中國醫療隊成員，以在疫情大流行期間最流行的見面禮「碰肘」代替握手，表示熱烈歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n從央視的畫面可見，武契奇轉身後，先親吻自己國家國旗，接着對一旁的中國五星旗，也獻上深情的一吻，表示對中國的感謝。<br />\n<br />\n這個舉動引發界兩極評論，有網民覺得「太過煽情」，也有人覺得是「真情表現」，因為直到目前為止，只有中國對他們伸出援手。亦有網民謂，中國當局隱瞞犯錯致武漢肺炎大爆發，疫情在全球擴散，塞爾維亞也無辜受害，中國給予這些援助也是補償而已，犯不着要如此矯情，猶如「斯德哥爾摩症候群」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這次中國赴塞爾維亞支援抗疫的專家組共有6人，來自中山大學附屬第三醫院，專長包括傳染病防治、呼吸與危重症、感染、心理等專業。"},{"pid":"f2d71a63c87174b539fd3aac1fe4974fc2a6a9a6","tid":1939130,"uid":7609,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"錫完即刻中支那肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73684edca7204ddbd221accb2ae97b62ed34afd","tid":1939130,"uid":126621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"攪左一戰出黎<br />\n而家想攪三戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f02b4ee1f5469ae90ec38e4617f3b9f624d3a8f","tid":1939130,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=xgtrUTGYh-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxgtrUTGYh-4&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=4d572949\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=xgtrUTGYh-4</a>"},{"pid":"235ea5d5c836374d85336d2be704d05ac21c92d7","tid":1939130,"uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/224529_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F224529_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1d9c5bf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e0d53deb5f1e98fa9a299bdc8208bc71f460b","tid":1939130,"uid":10670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"塞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0df19884c771e0e88ded4738f3ad15fc04453e8","tid":1939130,"uid":3149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"祝佢被滅國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}